---
description: "Prevents silent exceptions and empty catch statements"
globs: ["**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: false
---
# Exception Specification & Safety Guards
- You must NEVER generate or permit empty `catch` blocks. 
- Every `catch` block must explicitly handle or log the error using a dedicated logger or reporter.
- If an exception cannot be safely recovered, it must be thrown up the call stack to prevent silent system degradation.
